docstring:
"""
Form Widget classes specific to the Django admin site.
"""

classes.docstring:
"""
    A SelectMultiple with a JavaScript filter interface.

    Note that the resulting JavaScript assumes that the jsi18n
    catalog has been loaded in the page
    """
classes.name: FilteredSelectMultiple

classes.docstring:
"""
    A SplitDateTime Widget that has some admin-specific styling.
    """
classes.name: AdminSplitDateTime

classes.docstring:
"""
    A Widget for displaying ForeignKeys in the "raw_id" interface rather than
    in a <select> box.
    """
classes.name: ForeignKeyRawIdWidget

classes.docstring:
"""
    A Widget for displaying ManyToMany ids in the "raw_id" interface rather than
    in a <select multiple> box.
    """
classes.name: ManyToManyRawIdWidget

classes.docstring:
"""
    This class is a wrapper to a given widget to add the add icon for the
    admin interface.
    """
classes.name: RelatedFieldWidgetWrapper

classes.docstring:
"""
    Select widget mixin that loads options from AutocompleteJsonView via AJAX.

    Renders the necessary data attributes for select2 and adds the static form
    media.
    """
classes.name: AutocompleteMixin
